title: Electrolux Refrigerator Door Shelf Bin
description: Electrolux Refrigerator Door Shelf Bin ★★★★★ ★★★★★ 148 Reviews PartSelect Number PS429873 Manufacturer Part Number 240338101 This retainer bar (Refrigerator Door Shelf Bin, Refrigerator Door Shelf, Door Shelf Bin, Refrigerator Door Bin) holds items on the refrigerator door shelf. The plastic retainer can become brittle with time and crack or break under the strain of normal use. It can also break if heavy items are placed in the door shelf. If this part will no longer hold securely onto the inner door panel it will need to be replaced. This model is white plastic, and measures 26 by 5 inches. Sold individually.
